{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In &quot;Grocery Store Simulator&quot; you take on the role of a grocery store manager. It's a first-person game where you handle every aspect of running a grocery business. From working the checkout to managing stock in the warehouse, each choice you make affects your store\u2019s success. Play by yourself or with friends in online co-op mode to expand your store and improve your management skills. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961880/extras/StoreManagement_Separator.png?t=1734205616\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Place your store equipment anywhere you want, check out customer items, make sure your pricing is right, and keep shelves stocked to keep customers happy. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961880/extras/RS_StoreManagement.gif?t=1734205616\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961880/extras/CoopGameplay_Separator.png?t=1734205616\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Team up with your friends online in a 4 player co-op mode to run your store together, sharing tasks and strategies to boost profits.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961880/extras/RS_Coop.gif?t=1734205616\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961880/extras/InventoryControl_Separator.png?t=1734205616\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Order new products, manage deliveries, and keep your warehouse organized to efficiently use the limited space and meet the daily needs of your store. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961880/extras/RS_InventoryManagement.gif?t=1734205616\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961880/extras/Customization_Separator.png?t=1734205616\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Personalize your store with any wallpaper you choose and give it a unique and memorable name. You can also decorate your store however you want!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961880/extras/RS_Customization.gif?t=1734205616\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"First Beeps","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2961880/f679b574285484cefb75d29b281ae7f6797a9ba2.jpg"},{"name":"I Think I'll Use My Credit Card","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2961880/1f1bcfcc10e30e7c8164cc0b8a23449d0f687474.jpg"},{"name":"I Hear Beeps in My Sleep","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2961880/b61e27e31ad9d2c3466d0c5bd6576bb47670bccc.jpg"},{"name":"And So It Begins","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2961880/f9f9e3a163c74e58e81174ea7b47ca7526cc2c86.jpg"},{"name":"Order, Order, Order","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2961880/8cbf76a4ce61169bed79cba089bf091d917388aa.jpg"},{"name":"Delivery Man's Favorite","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2961880/97c561c09eb6e0958e720674ebf7c539f81d1f91.jpg"},{"name":"Up and Coming","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2961880/09dedd83a79f4f9a1a5a3f29dd2c133229a5924b.jpg"},{"name":"Growth Spurt","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steam